xal.sim.slg

Interface VisitorListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BCMonitor, BLMonitor, BPMonitor, BSMonitor, Dipole, Drift, EDipole, EKicker, Element, EQuad, HSteerer, Marker, Octupole, PermMarker, Quadrupole, RFGap, Sextupole, SkewQuad, SkewSext, Solenoid, ThinElement, VSteerer, WScanner

    public interface VisitorListener
    Objects implementing VisitorListener can be called to accept a Visitor.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void accept(Visitor v)
      When called with a Visitor reference the implementor can either reject to be visited (empty method body) or call the Visitor by passing its own object reference.

    • Method Detail

      • accept

        void accept(Visitor v)
        When called with a Visitor reference the implementor can either reject to be visited (empty method body) or call the Visitor by passing its own object reference.
        Parameters:
        v - the Visitor which wants to visit this object.
